4ï¸âƒ£ Task vs Service (important distinction)
Task	Service
One run	Long-running
No auto-restart	Auto-restart
Jobs / batch	APIs / consumers

ğŸ”¥ Interview tip:

â€œServices maintain desired count of tasks.â€

5ï¸âƒ£ How this maps to your system
Rails Task Definition

Image: rails-api

Port: 3000

Env: DB, secrets

Command: Puma

Elixir Task Definition

Image: elixir-consumer

CPU heavy

Command: mix run --no-halt

